    "title": "How Do I Automate Client Intake for My Accounting Firm",
    "slug": "how-do-i-automate-client-intake-for-my-accounting-firm",
    "metaDescription": "How to automate client intake for your accounting firm. Collect information and documents automatically with intelligent intake workflows.",
