    "solutionOverview": "Reducing month-end work for bookkeepers is about identifying which tasks are truly manual and which are manual only because no one has taken the time to systematize them. When bank reconciliations pull data automatically, standard adjusting entries are templated, and client reporting follows a consistent format, the per-client effort drops significantly. The goal is a month-end process that scales with your client count without requiring proportionally more hours.",
