        "description": "We sit down with your team and walk through the daily, weekly, and seasonal tasks that consume the most time. The goal is to identify specific bottlenecks where AI tools are most likely to deliver noticeable relief, not to catalog every possible use case.",
        "subheading": "Assessment"
