    "heroSubtitle": "Coordinate your accounting firm's social media presence and email marketing into a single automated system where both channels reinforce each other and run consistently without demanding constant attention from your team.",
    "heroDescription": "Accounting firms that try to maintain both a social media presence and an email marketing program often find themselves doing neither one well. Social posts go out sporadically when someone remembers, emails get drafted but never sent, and there is no real strategy connecting the two channels. The result is inconsistent visibility and missed opportunities to stay in front of both prospects and existing clients. When social media and email automation are managed as a coordinated system, your firm maintains a consistent presence across multiple channels with far less manual effort. Social content and email campaigns share a common messaging strategy, prospect engagement on one channel can trigger follow-up on the other, and your team gains a reliable marketing engine that runs in the background while they focus on serving clients.",
