        "description": "Rather than relying on team members to check whether a prior step is complete before starting the next one, workflow automation moves documents through your defined sequence automatically. When source documents are marked complete, preparation can begin. When preparation is finished, the return routes to review. Each step triggers the next without manual intervention."
