        "title": "Eliminate Manual Data Transfers Between Applications",
        "description": "When your client accounting software does not talk to your document management platform, someone on your team is copying information between them. That manual step introduces delays, errors, and an invisible cost that compounds with every client and every engagement. Integration removes that step entirely by automating the data handoff."
