    "heroDescription": "Most solo CPAs know they should be doing more marketing, but the reality is that client work always takes priority. That means referrals dry up between busy seasons, past clients forget about advisory services you offer, and prospects who inquired months ago never heard back. Marketing automation built specifically for a solo CPA practice addresses this by running targeted, personalized outreach on your behalf. It sends the right message at the right time to the right contact, so your practice stays visible and your pipeline stays warm even when you are deep in returns or audit prep.",
