    "heroDescription": "Solo accountants often rely on a mix of email, text messages, shared drives, and phone calls to communicate with clients and exchange documents. It works, but it does not scale well, and it does not project the level of professionalism that attracts and retains higher-value clients. A client portal designed for solo accounting practices changes that dynamic entirely. Clients get a single, branded destination where they can upload documents, view the status of their engagements, access completed deliverables, send secure messages, and manage their account information. For you, it means fewer scattered communications to track, fewer document-chasing emails to send, and a client experience that builds loyalty and generates referrals.",
