        "answer": "Adoption depends largely on the experience you create and how you introduce it. We design portals that are intuitive enough for clients who are not particularly tech savvy, and we help you develop an introduction approach that positions the portal as a benefit to the client rather than just a convenience for you. Most practitioners find that once clients use the portal for their first document upload or status check, they prefer it to the old way of doing things.",
