        "answer": "Marketing automation can actually be more impactful for smaller firms because you are likely the one doing everything, and any time you reclaim from manual marketing tasks goes directly back into revenue generating work. The key is selecting tools and workflows that match your scale. We would not recommend enterprise level platforms for a sub million dollar firm. Instead, we focus on right sized solutions that deliver meaningful results without unnecessary complexity or cost.",
        "category": "General"
